      • transformParts

        public void transformParts(org.eclipse.uml2.uml.Class compositeImplementation)
        If the bootloader is responsible for creating an instance (if it is a abstract type), do nothing since the part is already a reference in Java. If the composite is responsible, add a default value that creates the sub-instances.
